						               													<description>MAKIN' MOVIES is a card game about collecting the right actors and money to make a movie.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;  You are a low budget movie producer and your goal is to compete against other players to be the first to collect enough money and the right actors to make your movie.  Use your money to protect your actors from other players, or hire their actors!  It's a simple card game with many options and different ways to win. &amp;#10; Each turn every player has 3 actions which represent; Holding auditions, casting for roles in your movie and hiring actors from other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game concludes with the winning player naming their movie or giving a quick advertisement trailer for their movie based on the strange collection of actors they have hired.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The FREE Print and Play game contains 44 actor cards, 12 money cards, 8 scripts.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Retail Version contains 50 actors, 12 money cards, and 10 scripts.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
